理は、こども未来戦略会議において、学校給食費の無償化に向けて、全国…", "…感にさいなまれた社会に風穴を空けるべく全力を尽くすことをお誓い申し上げて、私の質問を終わります。（拍手）〔内閣総理大臣岸田文雄君登壇、拍手〕"]}]}, {"meeting_name": "参議院 東日本大震災復興特別委員会", "remarks": [{"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/35", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/37", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/39", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/41", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/43", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/45", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/47", "sentence": ["…避難に活用という点では、気象庁の線状降水帯予測というのがございます。岸田総理は、昨年の臨時国会の所信表明演説で、線状降水帯の予測の高度化など…"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/49", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/51", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/53", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/55", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/57", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314858X00420240517/60", "sentence": []}]}]}, {"date": "2024-06-04", "meeting": [{"meeting_name": "参議院 内閣委員会", "remarks": [{"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314889X01820240604/41", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314889X01820240604/43", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314889X01820240604/45", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314889X01820240604/47", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314889X01820240604/49", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314889X01820240604/51", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121314889X01820240604/53", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/1